{"tid":947317,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[挑撥離間]中共反偷渡宣傳:《人間地獄——香港》","createTime":"2018-12-19T07:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T07:49:28.000Z","uid":119996,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e31ce30de4899c016639117d53689b496907b4a","tid":947317,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"中共反偷渡宣傳<br />\n當時，中國共產黨對香港進行醜化宣傳，發過一份文件，叫《人間地獄&mdash;&mdash;香港》，其中是如此描述：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港是世界上最荒淫的城市；</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港黑社會橫行；</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">香港是最大的製毒販毒基地；</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">香港自殺者是世界上有數的。</span><br />\n<br />\n由於香港在1997前不受中華人民共和國管治，中國大陸的政策如大躍進、上山下鄉及文化大革命影響不到香港，香港又處於經濟騰飛時期，所以香港人的生活水平，事實上比中國大陸高出了許多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%80%83%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=uKxilzV8Tp9rAPgAIDIpuRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=4486f663\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%80%83%E6%B8%AF</a><br />\n見到真係忍唔住POST,笑到我抽搐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.論荒淫,由細到大,都聽D大陸妹2奶點搞散人頭家,調轉真係少得多<br />\n2.曾經係既,某方向報紙,某電影公司等等,童黨<br />\n而家黑社會賣飯盒比地盤都比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3.可能而家都係,香港係世界聞名轉口港,但係我唔食,好多人都唔食,WFC<br />\n4.不嬲都係,壓力大,但點解D人比鯊魚咬比差佬捉都要落香港?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論:共匪一無是處"},{"pid":"5ecfb6e304bebc5ac2fca5c3c6b97b24ddc63320","tid":947317,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:42:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cc1af34f73ad37080498409ecb6a8dd1385a96e","tid":947317,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港好撚垃圾<br />\n支那蝗快啲死返上去住"},{"pid":"67d3d2b0f44b4d89a704c6150c6b873e880172b2","tid":947317,"uid":124430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:45:10.000Z","msg":"幾廿年前嘅嘢仲講嚟做乜"},{"pid":"63e780f5880313f6d6a132033dc4241df7cfcf12","tid":947317,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d3d2b0f44b4d89a704c6150c6b873e880172b2","tid":947317,"uid":124430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:45:10.000Z","msg":"幾廿年前嘅嘢仲講嚟做乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"中共做乜成日講南京大屠殺"},{"pid":"9e8b6beca72aadd5de867bfcd3bf4eef744fc63a","tid":947317,"uid":124430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63e780f5880313f6d6a132033dc4241df7cfcf12","tid":947317,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d3d2b0f44b4d89a704c6150c6b873e880172b2","tid":947317,"uid":124430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:45:10.000Z","msg":"幾廿年前嘅嘢仲講嚟做乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"中共做乜成日講南京大屠殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"點知鄰國點解要咁做啫"},{"pid":"e4501ff12cc2bff70275dd7837d56ee70825a193","tid":947317,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d3d2b0f44b4d89a704c6150c6b873e880172b2","tid":947317,"uid":124430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:45:10.000Z","msg":"幾廿年前嘅嘢仲講嚟做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:48:37.000Z","msg":"幾廿年前都可以咁樣抹黑<br />\n而家到手仲唔玩死?<br />\n睇路啊,清"},{"pid":"00d472314751149f193a8dd94c24f9783b6f94fd","tid":947317,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:49:28.000Z","msg":"香港自殺者是世界上有數的<br />\n<br />\n反之 中國人自殺係唔會有實際數字架"}]}